EASTERN MEDITERRANEAN SEA.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY 23 JUN THRU 15 JUL BY
   M/V MINERVA UNO TOWING ONE MILE
   LONG CABLE IN AREA BOUND BY
   34-33.0N 014-35.5E, 34-31.5N 014-48.8E,
   34-38.3N 014-49.9E, 34-48.6N 014-39.0E,
   34-48.6N 014-30.3E, 34-43.9N 014-23.8E.
   TWO MILE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 16 JUL 13.
